high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the door. Turn right at the door and walk to the right side of the desk.
Pick up the box from the top shelf of the desk.
Turn to the left and walk to the bedside table with box in hand.
Turn the lamp on the top shelf of the desk, to your right on.
Turn right, cross the room, hang a left at the door and walk to the wooden dresser ahead.
Pick up the brown clock from the top shelf of the desk.
Turn around, hang a right around the chair of the desk and turn right at the bed to face the desk.
Turn on the small lamp on the left side of the shelf on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a clock by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk toward the door, then left and over to the desk
Pick up the alarm clock from the desk
Turn left and walk to the lamp slightly left on the desk
anns.task_desc: Examine the alarm clock under the light of the lamp
